Hibernate is connects the Java objects to database table by using entity class and annotation.

Main Annotation used in Hibernate 
@Entity and @Id  
Entity is used to map Java class to Database table 
Id is used to set the primary key in the table.  field entity  set as a primary key

EntityManagerFactory -> establish connection with database
Entitymanager -> Interact with Database by performing the crud operation of Insert, Update, delete , Saves the data

//persist()
find()
//remove()
//merge()
Entitytransaction -> control the transaction. 



